Aqua Teen Hunger Force, retitled Aqua Unit Patrol Squad 1 in 2011[1] and Aqua Something You Know Whatever in 2012,[2] is an American animated television series on Cartoon Network's late night programing block, Adult Swim, as well as Teletoon's Teletoon at Night block and later G4 Canada's ADd block in Canada. It is one of the spin-offs of Space Ghost Coast to Coast, and as of 2012, the longest running original series on Adult Swim as well as being amongst the top 10 longest-running American animated television series of all time.[3]
